Prey: mites, spiders, plant lice, snails, slugs
Fun Fact: Survives freezing temperatures by producing glycerol and maintaining slower metabolic processes
Most Distinctive Feature: Change color based on temperature and activity

Age of Weaning: 45 to 65 days for metamorphosis from tadpole
Name: Gray Tree Frog
